description: Officials decided to move the woman after she went into labour on Italy's Lampedusa island.
title: Lampedusa: Migrant with coronavirus gives birth in helicopter
title_page: Lampedusa: Migrant with coronavirus gives birth in helicopter - BBC News
maintext: "The crew have done their best to make life as acceptable as possible but it's not conditions you can offer anyone for this extended period of time," he said.
